r: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">临沣寨</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;全国重点文物保护单位，第一批中国传统古村落，第二批中国历史文化名村，建村较早。明清古建筑连片成群，“五脊六兽硬山顶、青砖浮雕莲花脊”，寨内建筑极具河南民居风格，具有极高的建筑史学价值。现存明清及传统建筑共计297栋926间，其中明清建筑175栋562间，传统建筑122栋364间。中央电视台《走遍中国》《百科探秘》《远方的家》摄制组先后在此拍摄专题片并在中央电视台播放。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span data-ratio=\"1.7666666666666666\" id=\"js_tx_video_container_0.6748657097278392\" class=\"js_tx_video_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: block; width: 678px !important; height: 382px !important;\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" width=\"678\" height=\"381.375\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?origin=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com&vid=r0624516276&autoplay=false&full=true&show1080p=false&isDebugIframe=false\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></iframe></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span data-ratio=\"1.7666666666666666\" class=\"js_tx_video_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 677px !important; height: 381px !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565228656583.jpg\" title=\"1560565228656583.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">&nbsp; 临 沣寨 简 介</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">临沣寨位于河南省平顶山市郏县堂街镇，东高西低，包括平、沙、山、岗、五种地形。&quot;紫云晴雪&quot;被列为郏县八大景之首，被誉为&quot;中原第一红石古寨&quot;、&quot;村寨博物馆&quot;，有&quot;汝河南岸第一府&quot;之称。临沣寨坐落在碧波荡漾的北汝河畔，发源于香山的利溥、沣溪两水分别从寨东寨西流过，流向北汝河。整个村落被一种浅红色条石砌筑的寨墙紧紧围着，故当地人又称临沣寨叫&quot;红石寨&quot;或&quot;红石古寨&quot;。由临沣寨通往村外的是东、西、南三个寨门，其中西寨门取名&quot;临沣&quot;，东寨门取名&quot;溥滨&quot;，意为此寨濒临沣溪、利溥两水。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">东、西寨门由木板镶铁皮制成，至今仍保存完好;南寨门毁坏较重，只剩半个门洞。临沣寨为一洼地型古村落，周围千亩芦苇、百亩竹园。杨柳河、北汝河绕寨而过，终年绿水长流。寨内还有较为完整的清代四合院、三合院20多座，清代民居近400间。这些建筑既有中原农村特有的以砖、石为主体的高大深邃，也有南方以木格子门窗为装饰的小巧玲珑。一些古老的宅院用多层弧形石板作为门洞的拱顶，每层石板上都雕有图案，十分美观。墙、古寨河、明清时期古民居、宗祠、关帝庙融为一体，成为中原民居文化中一块不可多得的文化瑰宝。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565241333479.jpg\" title=\"1560565241333479.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565249828970.jpg\" title=\"1560565249828970.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;传统建筑与朱宅</span></span></p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">临沣寨百分之九十为朱姓人家，所以以前临沣寨又叫朱家洼。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">临沣寨传统建筑规模宏大，类型齐全。这些<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">建筑从明代晚期一直延续到现在，且在各个时间段上均有标志性建筑。寨内有红石砌筑的明代民居，有汝河南岸第一府———朱镇府古建筑群，有重修于咸丰年间的关帝庙，有保存尚好的古四合院建筑，这些古民居建筑群除少部分被后人拆除或翻新外，大部分保存了原有风貌，是一座古代建筑活化石库。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565291145685.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565291145685.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565291302845.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565291302845.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565291703391.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565291703391.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565291475910.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565291475910.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565291572508.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565291572508.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">临沣寨建筑，多为砖木青瓦房，属明清四合院建筑。所有的建筑群沿中轴线对称而建（大多数根据《营造法式》），坐北朝南，冬避寒冷，夏迎清凉。地基由寨子附近紫云山特产的红石精雕细磨垒砌而成，因此，至今地基无变形，房屋坚固如初。在湖南大学柳肃教授讲的《中国古代建筑艺术》中介绍道，古代建筑侧面的墙叫做山墙，临沣寨古代建筑每个山墙上都有代表中国传统的“福禄寿禧”文化的字符，整块红石透雕而成的窗户坚固大方。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565330660941.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565330660941.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565330974252.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565330974252.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565330970212.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565330970212.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">在传统民居建筑中，除了房屋进数（二、三、四等），开间数（3、5、7、9），屋顶样式（悬山，庑殿，歇山，攒尖等）代表身份以外，附在建筑上的各类装饰也体现出主<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">人的社会地位、财富和审美情趣等。民居中的门脸、檐廊、屋顶、斗拱，开窗等都是其重点装饰的部位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">临沣古建筑内现存的匾额，其书写方式、刻写工艺均依内容而定，楷、草、行、篆、隶等各体兼备。厅堂中的堂匾用楷书和隶书，寨门匾用楷书，府厅匾则一定是用楷书，黑底金字，显得庄严肃穆。像朱镇府内的月亮门匾则用篆书，显得主人文化品位高。主体建筑脊檩上的题记，就成了断定该建筑物的主人和建筑年代的依据，具有极高的文物价值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565341398913.jpg\" title=\"1560565341398913.jpg\" alt=\"13.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">明清古建筑是清一色的木构架，石雕、砖雕、木雕成为村中古建筑装饰的一大特色。但是寨中明清建筑上的砖雕、木刻，基本上没有一件是完全相同的。明代木雕多在显眼之处，题材多为植物纹样或瑞兽图案；清代木雕则包括飞禽走兽、神话传说、戏曲故事、人物花鸟、文房四宝等。雕刻技法多种多样，浮雕，透雕同时运用。有时一件雕刻品上，往往多种工艺并用。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565353266096.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565353266096.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565353396388.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565353396388.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565353564369.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565353564369.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565353449622.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565353449622.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"> 现在的工艺水平也能做出如此精美的木雕砖雕工艺品，但是作为明清时代的工艺技术和科技水平，完全是手工制作，所以显得异常珍贵。明清之际是很注重装饰物的配饰的，就像前文说到那样，那是身份和文化修养的体现。在朱紫峰府的家具中，无论是茶桌的装饰，还是椅子靠背处的浮雕刻画，抑或是床的装扮，无不体现地位的显著。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565369527659.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565369527659.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565369350556.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565369350556.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">&nbsp;临 &nbsp;沣 &nbsp;寨 &nbsp;墙</span></span></p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">根据历史记载，临沣寨初修筑于清道光年间，完工于同治元年。清政府为对付太平军和捻军，在河南各乡村推行修筑圩寨措施。临沣寨是依托自然村庄而建，同时也体现了聚族而居的村落组织传统，是当时寨堡的典型代表。临沣寨寨墙用红石砌筑，白灰勾缝，建有垛子，哨楼，森严壁垒。每个寨门上都有灭火水槽，还有用于对外射击的高低不等的枪眼，寨外有护寨河，临沣溪水汇入护寨河，与红石寨墙共同构成一道坚固的防御体系，具有防御战乱和洪水的功能。随着时间的推移，护寨河已然干涸，跟历史记载的深宽度也发生了变化。而现在护寨墙成了当地村民的早上和傍晚散步的场所。在我以往的旅行中也见过很多古城墙，开封的古城墙，赣州宋城古城墙，登封古城墙，但大多数是青砖白缝，或者残败不堪，红砖白缝的“城墙”算是第一次见了，虽然它只是护寨墙，却也五脏俱全，具有防御功能，临沣寨被誉为“中原第一红石古寨”。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565381924919.jpg\" title=\"1560565381924919.jpg\" alt=\"20.jpg\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">红砖白缝，高低不同的枪眼</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565392994687.jpg\" title=\"1560565392994687.jpg\" alt=\"21.jpg\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">垛子哨楼</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565406346446.jpg\" title=\"1560565406346446.jpg\" alt=\"22.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"> 左边是依稀可见的护寨河（干涸），右边是寨墙。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565418434092.jpg\" title=\"1560565418434092.jpg\" alt=\"23.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>',122,0,NULL),(28,1,'特色民宿和大型房车露营基地落户平顶山！',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560565808','/uploads/20190615/3fc51f1deba2388ce2443669e216f5f2.png','<p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565727301829.jpg\" title=\"1560565727301829.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">重磅消息！5月30日上午，在河南省旅游服务中心，平顶山市文化广电和旅游局同河南赢合文旅产业发展有限公司签订战略合作协议，郏县姚庄回族乡张布郎村与河南赢合文旅产业发展有限公司签订正式落地协议。在不久的时间里，各式房车、星空水晶屋、五彩树屋、精致红酒杯屋、玻璃穹顶观星花房、鲜花主题餐饮、四季冲浪泳池等精品特色文旅项目将落户平顶山。</p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565736704776.jpg\" title=\"1560565736704776.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">本次签约的张布郎自然村位于姚庄回族乡小张庄村东部，辖2个村民小组，450口人，回汉杂居，陡沟河环村而过。村内拥有明清两代古建筑多处，传统建筑210多间。传说明朝时候，村里出了个侍郎（布郎）官，这位张姓官员平生待人“诚一不伪”，生活“节俭不奢”，为了回报家乡，他组织群众兴修水利，修堰屯田，造福乡里。后来，人们为了纪念他，就以他的官衔命名该村为张布郎村。这里是远近闻名的长寿村，全村现有90岁以上老人16位，其中河南省最年长的118岁张学礼老人就生活在这里。</p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">根据规划，签约项目将依托本村现有的自然资源与历史人文资源，打造以“活百岁”为主题的回家民宿，对现有破旧民房进行装修改造，打造经典北方民居特色的回家民宿，打造以张学礼老人为代表的“活百岁”品牌文化以及德孝文化体验教育基地等项目，以文旅项目带动当地特色老茶馆体验文化，美食文化，非遗文化发展，进而带动当地特色产业经济发展。</p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">张布郎存村改造效果图：</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565756271621.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565756271621.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565756332035.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565756332035.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565756212283.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565756212283.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565756973955.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565756973955.jpg\"/></p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">据了解，河南赢合文旅产业发展有限公司注册资金1亿元，是一家专注文化和旅游项目开发、规划建设、投资运营、景区托管为一体的文化旅游产业融合发展的文旅产业发展公司。公司现已与鲁山县签订了鲁山牛郎织女风情园房车露营酒店、尧山花海星空民宿及房车露营基地、天龙池雾海房车露营基地、桑盘织女家民宿产业园等项目。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565786799767.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565786799767.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565786228184.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560565786228184.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">上述每个项目都会在当地成立项目公司，采取与当地景区或者村集体合作，让合作方成为公司股的运营模式，带动当地的土特产、农副产品、手工艺品的市场推广及传统非遗文化传承与保护等，对实现文旅带动脱贫攻坚、文旅推动乡村振兴具有重要意义。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565798551843.jpg\" title=\"1560565798551843.jpg\" alt=\"10.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560565803356641.png\" title=\"1560565803356641.png\" alt=\"11.png\"/></p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">记者在现场还打探到重要消息：该公司将在平顶山建中原地区最大的房车露营基地和房车博览交易中心，第一批房车营地有望于今年国庆节前建成营业，届时，自行式房车、露营式房车、拖挂式房车将由您自由选择，怎么样，有没有很期待？</p><p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">在签约现场， 因为看中了与我市文旅项目合作的前景，河南乐活旅游开发有限公司、河南宇通客车股份有限公司、河南柏川古建园林绿化工程有限公司、河南保税跨境电子商务有限公司、郑州弘冠珠宝销售销售有限公司等十家企业与河南赢合文旅产业发展有限公司签订合作协议，将形成合力，带动我市全域旅游发展。</p><p><br/></p>',192,0,NULL),(29,1,'郏县茨芭镇北竹园村沟东自然村，一个藏在深山里的僻静小村',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560566109','/uploads/20190615/d3658d21df58cf3325acc817917c5261.jpeg','<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">村民们住的窑洞改成农家院</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566046222766.jpeg\" title=\"1560566046222766.jpeg\" alt=\"1.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">原先是土窑，后来用青石券成石窑</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566057743020.jpeg\" title=\"1560566057743020.jpeg\" alt=\"2.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">窑高可分两层，上层住人，放杂物</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566062599201.jpeg\" title=\"1560566062599201.jpeg\" alt=\"3.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">这是民国时期的村里的蹚将魏国柱曾住过的窑洞</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566067803760.jpeg\" title=\"1560566067803760.jpeg\" alt=\"4.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">民国期魏国柱藏枪的地方</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566072489811.jpeg\" title=\"1560566072489811.jpeg\" alt=\"5.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">足有五尺长的一个道道，当时可是在床边的。</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566078213610.jpeg\" title=\"1560566078213610.jpeg\" alt=\"6.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">记有魏国柱名字的石碑</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566083246174.jpeg\" title=\"1560566083246174.jpeg\" alt=\"7.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">村里老人谈当年村里的英雄人物</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566088248891.jpeg\" title=\"1560566088248891.jpeg\" alt=\"8.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">还留存着农耕那种平静的生活</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566093297238.jpeg\" title=\"1560566093297238.jpeg\" alt=\"9.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">时不时有外地人来采风</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566098179349.jpeg\" title=\"1560566098179349.jpeg\" alt=\"10.jpeg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>',147,0,NULL),(30,1,'河南平顶山：城区里的古宅院',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560566319','/uploads/20190615/505357e17fdb78d58913e596d1de9284.png','<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">河南省平顶山市湛河区马庄街道有个陈家大院，虽然四周高楼林立，但它却被保存得相对完好。2016年，这处古宅院被列为“省级文物保护单位”。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">这个古宅院位于西铁炉社区，系当地陈氏第三代传人建于清雍正八年（公元1730年），至今已有300多年历史。大院并列两排，一进三院，过去的后花园有亭台楼阁，现仍保存完好的房间有78间（原有房屋136间），有些房屋至今仍住有人家。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566292322805.png\" title=\"1560566292322805.png\" alt=\"1.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">古宅全景</p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566301482413.png\" title=\"1560566301482413.png\" alt=\"2.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">古老的小巷折射着历史的沧桑</p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566309573435.png\" title=\"1560566309573435.png\" alt=\"3.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">村民们走过小巷，似乎穿越到了久远的过去</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">城中村改造中，当地有关部门采取有效措施对这处古宅院进行保护，并把其列为“省级旅游村”建设的重要组成部分。（原载于2016年11月29日《平顶山日报》5版）</p><p><br/></p>',128,0,NULL),(31,1,'河南平顶山：传说中的曹镇水席',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560566585','/uploads/20190615/bc8abf59a7fa0f7ed8b50f4b4cf5367a.png','<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">曹镇水席在河南省平顶山地区最为盛名，不仅在于其菜味独特，老少皆宜，更在于其与宋代的宫廷宴席有着莫大的关系。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566504360873.png\" title=\"1560566504360873.png\" alt=\"1.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">满桌正宗的曹镇水席菜</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong>曹娘娘与曹镇水席</strong><br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">相传北宋时期，宋真宗找朝中天师为自己算姻缘。天师夜观天象，说娘娘在汴京城南300里处。于是皇帝派钦差寻访娘娘。天师告诉钦差：“娘娘家房上的兽头是活的。”<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">钦差一路寻到了曹镇，路过一曹姓人家时，一只猫蹿上了房顶，趴在兽头的位置上。钦差便用轿迎回了这家唯一的女孩。这个女孩随后被宋真宗封为贤妃娘娘。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">曹娘娘出身贫困，吃不惯宫中的珍馐佳肴，加上思念家乡，入宫不到一年，竟得了病。宋真宗见状，特恩准她离宫回乡祭祖探亲。为答谢乡情，曹娘娘特带回一批御厨及大量珍稀食材，连日用好酒好菜犒劳家乡父老。看着众乡邻席间饕餮大吃、喜气洋洋的场景，曹娘娘很是开心，但依然不思茶饭。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566510711818.png\" title=\"1560566510711818.png\" alt=\"2.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">水席汤水多</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong>御厨做水席</strong><br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">一日，曹娘娘正在家同哥哥叙旧，厨房里忽然传来扑鼻香气，让曹娘娘顿生饿意。原来小侄子在沙河里摸了一条１公斤多的大鲤鱼，嫂子这会儿正忙着做红烧鱼。等嫂子把鱼端上，曹娘娘不顾吃相，一顿大吃，不一会儿就将红烧鱼吃得干干净净。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">曹娘娘的哥哥见状，把周边的有名厨师全部请到家中，要他们做拿手饭菜。负责曹娘娘膳食的公公见状，当即决定由当地厨师列出食材清单，由县太爷亲自负责选购，当地厨师和御厨一起造膳，把当地叫上名的菜品全部做出来。经过连夜准备，到第二天中午，各类菜品共做了二十余种，让曹娘娘食欲大增。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">看到曹娘娘吃得开心，公公特命令御厨把这些食材和做法记录下来带回宫廷，作为宫廷膳食专门伺候娘娘。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">由于曹娘娘是从水路回的家乡，又从水路回的京师，大家为纪念曹娘娘，遂把这道酒席叫做“水席”，意为从水路带来的宫廷宴席。由于历史久远，今人更习惯于从字面意思来理解水席，即主食一道热菜一道汤轮流而上，像流水一样不断更新。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">据传，宋真宗因喜爱水席，竟整日食宿于曹娘娘的寝宫。其他嫔妃得知，竞相派御厨学做水席，水席成为了北宋时期的一道宫廷名宴。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566517289365.png\" title=\"1560566517289365.png\" alt=\"3.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">时令蔬菜都是当地的特产</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong>曹镇水席与八仙桌</strong><br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">因为曹镇水席各类菜品的摆放位置及上席顺序一开始就按照八仙桌的格局进行设计，所以真正的曹镇水席文化是与八仙桌紧密相连的。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">水席一开始，先上八道凉菜，四荤四素，荤素相间摆放，分布四条边八个方位，代表阴阳相济，四象循环，八方相辅。主食居中摆放，代表中规中矩中庸之道。在八仙桌的四角分别摆上一小碟糖果，则是考虑到客人带有小孩儿，在没有正式开席之前，小孩儿可以先吃这些糖果。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">我国尊老、孝悌、敬客、谦卑观念，在“曹镇水席”的座次上得到了充分体现。主家宴客，每桌水席都专门放两张太师椅，为正座。正座又分为主座、陪座。坐正座的客人不论贫富和地位，只论辈分与年龄，一般是做客的长辈坐主座，由主家辈分相同，年龄相仿的人坐陪座作陪。正座的对面一般坐年轻小伙儿，主要负责端茶倒水，盛饭敬酒。除了小孩子外，每道菜上席之后，陪客要主动帮主座的长辈夹菜，长辈不动筷子后辈人都不允许动筷。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566523409121.png\" title=\"1560566523409121.png\" alt=\"4.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">厨师大多是当地农民</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong>水席菜品的寓意和选择</strong><br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">曹镇水席在传承中产生了很多约定俗成的规矩，不同场合的水席，对菜品要求也有所不同。婚宴的水席上必须有“两菜一汤”，两菜即“凉拌莲菜和糖醋鲤鱼”，寓意“喜结连理”。“一汤”即用红枣、花生、桂圆、莲子四种食材加红糖熬制而成，寓意“早生贵子”。另外，家中添丁置办宴席，主食的第一道荤菜必须为糖醋鲤鱼，寓意鱼跃龙门。家中添女置办宴席，主食的第一道荤菜必须为黄焖整鸡，寓意凤栖贵地。曹镇水席的最后一道菜都是用打散的鸡蛋熬制成的甜汤，意在含蓄地告诉大家已圆满散宴，客人们可以离席回家了。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">曹镇水席对不同食材的选择要求也比较严格。当地水席圈流传着这样一句谚语“斤半鲤鱼马蹄鳖，一拃（长度）蹿条（小鱼）一寸虾（当地读“虾”为“xie”），斤鸡炖汤糯米接”，说的就是，一斤半的鲤鱼一般需要三年长成，马蹄大小的河鳖一般需要五年长成，一斤重的土鸡一般半年长成，这个时候肉质正嫩，营养价值最高。一拃长的小鱼和一寸长的小虾炸好后，不用去刺剥皮，最为焦香可口。蒸糯米一般紧接在这几道菜之后上席。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566529860960.png\" title=\"1560566529860960.png\" alt=\"5.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">诱人的蒸碗</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">如今，水席的规格也根据客人的数量而发生了变化。过去的水席又叫“八大件”，即八道凉菜、八道热菜（又称干菜）、八道汤，外加两份面点。后来，简省到了“六大件”“四大件”。甚至还针对家庭聚餐、三到四人的朋友聚会还推出了“两大件”。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><div></div><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566534328647.png\" title=\"1560566534328647.png\" alt=\"6.png\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\">水果汤是孩子们的最爱</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">一千多年来，曹镇水席一直在河南民间广为流传，并逐渐形成“咸辣酸甜，四味俱全，香而不腻，醇厚悠长”的独特风味。如今，不少平顶山人扛起曹镇水席这一文化品牌到全国各地开饭店，备受当地消费者欢迎，因为他们推广的不只是水席产业，更是一部饱含历史印记的水席文化。<br data-node-type=\"Break\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（原载于2017年6月29日《平顶山日报》6版）</p><p><br/></p>',148,0,NULL),(32,1,'搞旅游 开民宿 襄城县雷洞村谋发展别有洞天',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560566759','/uploads/20190615/d4e4eaf78af2f74cdcdececaa1dcdfb3.jpg','<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">猛犸新闻·东方今报记者韩争强 &nbsp;文图</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566734413686.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566734640491.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（红石村——襄城县紫云镇雷洞）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">红石房、红石墙、红石路、红石磙、红石磨盘、红石渡槽、红石炕烟房、红石猪圈、红石厕所……在许昌市襄城县祡云山北麓有个古朴的村庄，与别的村不同，这里除了满目的青翠就是红石世界，它就是雷洞村。近几年，在当地政府牵头打造、扶持下，雷洞村立足本村特色，依靠发展乡村旅游，开设民宿，闯出了一片天，正吸引着越来越多的游客，前来这个“世外桃源”观光、游玩。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">5月8日，东方今报·猛犸新闻记者专程来到这里，亲身体验山村美景，深入探访这一生态旅游促进乡村振兴的鲜活典型。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">今昔对比&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;穷山沟变成“金窝窝”</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">从襄城县城驱车沿S329省道西行不到10分钟，向左拐上一条新修的柏油公路，就能看到路口用红石砌成、上刻“红石情怀，山水紫云”篆体大字的塔型路标和刻有“雷洞村”字样的长方形村标。车行道中，远山近水满目葱茏，七彩斑斓的风车长廊摇曳生辉，漫山遍野的鲜花五颜六色迎风怒放，山坡上“绿水青山就是金山银山”的巨型白色标语在蓝天白云和绿树芳草的映衬下熠熠闪光。这便是雷洞村了。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">雷洞村位于伏牛山东麓的襄城县紫云镇西南部，南邻平顶山市，西与宝丰县、郏县相邻，居三县交界处，毗邻紫云山景区，下辖6个自然村，分别坐落于半山腰和山谷底，全村共203户，622人，耕地面积580亩。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">“雷洞，雷洞。莫不是姓雷的人家早年因为穷建不起房子，在这里挖洞居住而得名？”“你的猜想很正确！”襄城县雷洞旅游开发有限公司经理李洋解答了记者对雷洞村名由来的疑惑。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">据当地村民介绍，雷洞村，东有小河、东南有水库，村落选址符合中国传统风水“背山面水”的理念，可谓风水宝地。但这个“风水宝地”却让雷洞村民挨饿受穷好多年。“饿死不嫁穷雷洞，雷洞光棍儿扎成堆！”20世纪六七十年代，在襄城县，这样的一句俗语广为流传。很多年来，雷洞村几乎就是穷山沟的代名词。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566734665628.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（掩映在青山绿水中的雷洞村）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">近几年来，雷洞村在上级党委、政府的大力支持、帮助、关心下，依托紫云山风景区资源优势，以独有的&quot;红石文化&quot;为基础，探索&quot;旅游&nbsp;扶贫&quot;模式，不仅实现了2016年整村脱贫，还让群众享受绿色生态发展红利，出现了“家家无闲人，人人有钱赚”的良好局面。昔日的穷山沟，现在变成了每天收金进银的“金窝窝”。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">立足特色 &nbsp;&nbsp;“靠山吃山”闯新路</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">雷洞村为啥这几年变化这么大？已在这里驻村近5年、对雷洞村变迁了如指掌的第一书记薛斌伟告诉记者，这主要是村里在上级党委政府指导下，确立了正确、科学的发展路子。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566735848053.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（红石墙、红石房、红石磨盘，用红石建造的村庄——雷洞）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566735239287.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（村庄小路——全部用古红石磨盘铺出来的）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">雷洞村四周红石遍地，先祖们当年在此居住以后，就地取材，利用红石建屋切墙，垒堰修渠，打石磨，凿石槽，繁衍生息，代代相传。如今，村内大面积、广泛保留有红石屋、红石墙、红石厕所、红石板路等红石建筑遗迹，“红石文化”已经深深地融入村民的生活之中。前些年，实施了封山育林，禁止采石，村民没了挣钱门路，许多青壮劳力只好外出打工，这里成了远近闻名的贫困村。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566735257356.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（山上的红石古寨）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566736549068.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（雷洞村一角）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">薛斌伟说，为了给乡亲们找到一条致富奔小康的新路，村里确立了“靠山吃山”，依托紫云山风景区和当地“古村、石寨、民宿、林果”的独特优势，大力发展 “特色农家乐&nbsp;林果采摘&nbsp;民宿”的生态旅游，促进农民增收，乡村振兴。今年4月30日，襄城县民宿产业发展启动仪式就在这里举行。仅今年“五一”小长假期间，这里接待的游客就将近有三万人（次），还有不少单位前来洽谈投资合作事宜。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">为了把旅游产业做大，把民宿品牌叫响，村里专门成立了集体企业——襄城县雷洞旅游开发有限公司。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566736347892.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（雷洞村一角）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">站在襄城县雷洞旅游开发有限公司前，放眼望去，斑驳的红石渡槽宛如长龙穿村而过，依山而建的古朴民居参差错落，掩映在遮蔽日的果树和翠竹之中，一条条平坦洁净的柏油路和水泥路如飘带般蜿蜒伸展，四通八达，红石磨盘铺就的步行甬路和风车造型的彩色小屋相映成趣。三五成群的游客们漫游其间，访古寨，赏美景，进农家，品美食，骋目抒怀，尽情游乐，歌声、笑声和百啭千鸣的鸟啼，宛若天籁，令人陶醉。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">顶层设计 &nbsp;&nbsp;“筑巢引凤”绘蓝图</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">谈笑间，忽闻远处传来高昂嘹亮的卡拉OK歌声，记者循声来到位于半山腰的一处小广场，只见一位头发灰白、精神矍铄的老人正随着音箱放出的伴奏，手持麦克放声高歌《在希望的田野上》，不少游客纷纷驻足倾听，不时报以热烈掌声。这位年近古稀的本村退休教师兴致勃勃地告诉记者，过去贫困的雷洞村能有如今的好光景，全靠党和政府乡村振兴的好政策，要不是政府修通了柏油路，这穷山沟啥时候也变不成“金窝窝”。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">正在村里规划照明亮化工程的紫云镇人大主席李占锋告诉记者，乡村振兴不能各自为政，一哄而上，必须做好顶层设计和规划引领。为了打造雷洞村这个全县的民宿旅游文化产业发展试点，镇党委、政府统筹谋划，同步实施了紫云山风景区开放式提升改造工程和占地1200亩、总投资12.13亿元、建筑面积约30万平方米的紫云谷新型养老基地一期项目，整合当地的优质自然资源和优势旅游资源，把雷洞村的民宿旅游融入全镇生态旅游的大格局中，加大扶持力度，加强基础建设投资，确保项目建设的高起点，高质量。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">为此，镇里专门聘请国内一流的设计公司制定《雷洞片区旅游规划》，在全村范围科学布局了采摘区、游览区、功能区、服务区，并先后投入巨资新修旅游公路23公里，修建了通往紫云书院的专用车道、步行阶梯和红石步道，以及风车、雕塑等区域景观小品。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;“栽下梧桐树，引来金凤凰”，优美的自然环境、独特的人文景观和日益完善的基础设施，不仅吸引了大批周边和外地游客前来观光游玩，而且也引起了众多投资方的合作兴趣。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">市场运营　突出民宿特色味道</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566736455900.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（老顽童家）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566737883474.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（游客在雷洞村游玩）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">在村民雷国栋的家，大门旁悬挂的木牌上书“老顽童家”，令人忍俊不已。从外表看，这是一个在外地极其少见的、由红石垒成的院墙、房屋的农家院子。屋檐下悬挂着一串串玉米和辣椒，散发着浓浓的乡土气息。推开古旧的屋门，内中更是别有乾坤，从顶到底全部是简约风格装修、设计。堂屋里摆放的木质沙发、茶几和左右两个卧室配置的双人床、衣柜，干净整洁，完全是宾馆套房的标准。装饰一新的西厢房里开放式餐厅、茶台和洗浴间一应俱全，东厢房里住着的房主雷国栋老两口呼之即来，可随时为客人提供餐饮、导游等各种服务，十分方便。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566737753948.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566737654539.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566737690571.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（室内装修设计如宾馆——简约又整洁）</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">李洋介绍，为了使这个民宿样板村走正路子，持续发展，村里一开始就成立了旅游服务公司，统一整合全村旅游资源，科学规划特色民宿，对现有民居分批分期实施改造，在保持古朴外貌和传统风格，“修旧如旧”的基础上进行内部装修和功能提升，让旅客在这里既能体验山村风味，又能享有方便舒适的居住条件。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566738513568.jpg\" width=\"1905 !important\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">李洋（右）在民宿——红石老匠家&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">目前，他们已经先期打造了5家样板民宿，每家的装修风格都各独具特色。由于实行了公司化、市场化的运营模式，村民以公司&nbsp;农户的方式，通过租赁、入股、分红等形式结成利益共同体，共享发展红利，深受群众欢迎，村民们纷纷申请尽快列入改造计划，并自愿将自家的老式家具和农耕器具无偿捐出，用于民宿改造。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">下一步，按照镇里规划，他们将积极寻求有实力的合作伙伴或投资方，加快民宿改建速度，提高基础设施标准和食宿接待能力，并对6个自然村现有的农家餐馆实施标准化改造，统一食材质量、餐饮卫生和价格，以优质服务擦亮“雷洞特色农家菜”的金字招牌。同时，充分发挥互联网和大数据的作用，积极开通网上订房业务和手机预定APP应用，精心打造涵盖周边景区的“一日游”、“二日游”线路，促进生态旅游和乡村振兴长盛不衰，良性发展，惠及更多农民。</p><p><br/></p>',188,0,NULL),(33,1,'探访郏县中顶莲花山',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560566941','/uploads/20190615/02d5e5d41bea126b08b3a6a583136da3.jpg','<p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566880499443.jpg\" title=\"1560566880499443.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">莲花山位于河南省郏县境内，因整个山体有五座山峰状如莲花，所以名为莲花山。它位于武当山金顶和辉县铁顶之间，又称中顶，他们并称三大道教圣地。据史料记载，公元491年，老子曾到此传道讲学。山顶北望，莲花山山脉连绵起伏，蜿蜒曲折，像一条巨龙盘旋在山水间。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566885647831.jpg\" title=\"1560566885647831.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">站在中顶眺望周围山峰如莲花花瓣</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566915371396.jpg\" title=\"1560566915371396.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">山顶怪石嶙峋，高低突兀，奇石间一条小道通往祖师庙。据当地人说，山上有一种石头内的图案酷似莲花盛开，是莲花山一大奇观，每逢夏季祖师庙内还会出现“祖师出汗、海马吐雾”等自然现象。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566919280897.jpg\" title=\"1560566919280897.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">莲花山有五座山峰，其中三座山峰上建有道观。主峰祖师庙，其他两座山峰分别是朝天宫和迎恩宫。据史料记载，这些道观建于北魏，已有千年历史。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566924444787.jpg\" title=\"1560566924444787.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">山顶平坦开阔，祖师庙内，环境优雅，树木参天，香火旺盛。两排古柏生长在庙内道路两侧，树枝和树干上系满了游客祈福的红布条，他们想通过这种形式，将美好的愿望变成现实，给他们带来好运。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566930135451.jpg\" title=\"1560566930135451.jpg\" alt=\"6.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">莲花山北麓，是五龙泉景区。在山体一侧有五支山泉分别从五条龙嘴内喷出。水质甘甜。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560566935362183.jpg\" title=\"1560566935362183.jpg\" alt=\"7.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">五龙泉前面有一池塘，涓涓细流汇入池内，泉水碧绿清澈，蓝天白云倒影其中</p><p><br/></p>',145,0,NULL),(34,1,'自驾游小伙河南信阳到四川安岳，不走高速能节约好多钱？',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560567287','/uploads/20190615/9f2cbdfac94d3019a7039a45ba8688a7.png','<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p08767gzgnz\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></p>',152,0,NULL);
INSERT INTO `ddsc_news` VALUES (35,1,'河南这几个“醉美”小镇，你去过几个？',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560567594','/uploads/20190615/43d75872467351c0509b839146355c7d.jpg','<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">河南这几个“醉美”小镇，你去过几个？</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">班家耕读小镇</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567507610005.jpg\" title=\"1560567507610005.jpg\" alt=\"u=3307631346,3340686750&amp;fm=173&amp;app=49&amp;f=JPEG.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">位于濮阳市卫都大街与S101交汇处，每当夜幕降临，濮阳市位于城乡一体化示范区的班家耕读镇就会穿上一件美丽的外衣：灯火通明，一串串的灯光就像天上落下的星星；水叮咚叮咚，一帧一帧的水仿佛在旋转时间匆匆……在水声的阴影下，无数的市民和游客聚集在一起，或停在商店门前，或停在大街小巷，附近班家村的村民都变成了厨师和店员，为人们提供传统的食物……</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567512662503.jpg\" title=\"1560567512662503.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">在班家耕读小镇，您可以领略江南古镇的古色古香，体验小桥流水的田园自然桃园生活，为疲惫的身心开启一段穿越时空的诗意之旅。班家村有着深厚的农耕文化。班家是在农耕文化的渗透和哺育下成长起来的。先是“无耕不食，无耕不衣”，后是“以耕养读，勤耕立家”，到最后的“耕者有其田”“耕读传家”，无不彰显着他们的勤劳、智慧、自强、自立。漫步小镇，避开城市的喧嚣，静静地享受乡村时光，漫步，聊天，品茶，发呆，打盹，在东篱下采摘菊花悠闲地看南山的心情会突然涌上心头。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">长寿山风情小镇</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567516485726.jpg\" title=\"1560567516485726.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">位于巩义市竹林镇，长寿山小镇位于长寿山景区310国道竹林镇。是集民俗表演、手工艺作坊、特色小吃、非物质文化遗产展示、民宿、酒吧、慢生活为一体的文化旅游项目。它是一个以“中原养生福地、栖息长寿山”为主题的文化景区。这里近距离望远山，徒步小径，绿树成荫，游人流连忘返。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567528904364.jpg\" title=\"1560567528904364.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">在小镇的民俗美食街，经营当地传统美食的店铺的开放式生产流程，就像民俗文化的表演，一个接一个的回归到原本的质朴，给人一种感官与精神的双重享受。八卦炉烤包子、客栈、陕西劙年、驴蹄面、廖花糖、菠萝饭等各种美食令过客过目难忘。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">西顶小镇</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567534226345.jpg\" title=\"1560567534226345.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">位于鹤壁市鹤山区西部山区，西丁小镇其实就是西顶村。它属于家属区西部，属于王家属村传统村落的“大洼地”。这里散布着石屋文化、石路、石巷、石墙、石屋、石院、石屋、石磨、石磨、石扇、石臼、石凳、石锅、石坝、石桥、石坡……上帝的吉石，斑驳成一道永不褪色的风景线。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567539374846.jpg\" title=\"1560567539374846.jpg\" alt=\"6.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">一座山，伫立在心灵的深处，缓缓地看花开花落，灯迎着风；一条河，浩浩荡荡的汤，在世界的外面蜿蜒前进；一座庙宇，井然有序，宁静在雾顶，梳理着风雨；一个舞台，诠释着这个世界，涂上了季节的色彩，熠熠生辉。来到西丁，吃了一顿热腾腾的饭，住了一晚的老炕，不知不觉觉得时间慢了很多。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">桑园小镇</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567543340145.jpg\" title=\"1560567543340145.jpg\" alt=\"7.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">位于鹤壁市淇滨区上峪乡悠悠淇水，巍巍太行，四周青山绿水，有一个美丽而古老的村庄，那就是桑园村。桑园镇距离鹤壁市中心22公里。它位于太行山东麓的浅山区，背靠南岭，脚临祁河。古镇古树参天，古屋别致，民风淳朴，风景秀丽。除了独特的古建筑群，还有六个文化主题房间，如农耕文化展示厅和娘桑民居，简约而富有魅力。住家区对游客来说既方便又实惠。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567547177835.jpg\" title=\"1560567547177835.jpg\" alt=\"8.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">桑园镇是引进100余种全国著名风味小吃，让您不仅能感受到古老的民俗风情，还能体会到舌尖上的愉悦。在商业区的小吃街，肉夹馍、羊肉面包汤和各种特色面食吸引着游客驻足品尝，民俗风情、工艺品等展览也深受游客青睐……</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">嵖岈山温泉度假小镇</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567553741452.jpg\" title=\"1560567553741452.jpg\" alt=\"9.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">位于驻马店市遂平县嵖岈山温泉小镇，嵖岈山温泉小镇坐落在美丽的山风景区，查雅天马湖，25公里远离遂平县城市，东邻107国道，京珠高速、京广铁路30分钟车程，北至郑州机场160公里，南至武汉330公里， 石武高速铁路纵向整个领土。嵖岈山温泉镇，以秀丽的嵖岈山自然风光为特色，以西游文化为内涵，以生态、美味为亮点，以温泉养生为主题的综合性观光度假小镇。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567558782330.jpg\" title=\"1560567558782330.jpg\" alt=\"10.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">嵖岈山温泉镇是集山地别墅、别墅会所、半岛别墅、游艇码头等为一体，打造生态生活的典范。嵖岈温泉城的运动水世界清凉的运动水，让炎热的气温向你告别，感受不同的夏日清凉。夏天到嵖岈温泉度假小镇住上一间木房，享受察雅山的美丽灯光，感受水的世界激情水，可以为夏天降温。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">花都温泉镇</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567563439318.jpg\" title=\"1560567563439318.jpg\" alt=\"11.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">位于许昌市鄢陵县陈化店镇，是集温泉、大型户外汤池、茶点、客房会议、保健娱乐为一体的旅游胜地。以温泉汤茶赏花为特色，以三国文化为基础，以休闲养生、生态旅游为内涵。它集成了水文化，花文化和茶文化，并把自然和生态森林和湖泊的形式出现，充分体现中国传统园林的精髓，集世界建筑的本质，强调自然与生态的主题，并创建一个简单而壮丽的自然景观。它不仅是一个田园诗般的地方，也是花、草、树和鸟的天堂。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567567436549.jpg\" title=\"1560567567436549.jpg\" alt=\"12.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">这里不仅空气清新，含氧量高，负离子浓度是城市的几倍；这里四季有花，四季有果，博大精深，绿水环绕，是健康、休闲、度假、旅游的理想圣地。在花都的温泉里，你可以在欢乐的海洋里向心爱的人表达你深深的爱，你可以穿着盛装在花海里浪漫的漫步。清澈的池水，洗去了夏日的疲惫，这里没有炎热，只有欢歌笑语，只有美好的生活回忆。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">白云小镇</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567583928724.jpg\" title=\"1560567583928724.jpg\" alt=\"13.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">位于洛阳市嵩县车村镇天桥沟村。“白云镇”是国家AAA级风景名胜区，位于河南“最美乡村”——天桥沟白云山脚下。距白云山8公里，木扎岭23公里。311国道贯穿全村，交通便利，最高海拔1800米，植被繁茂，森林覆盖率达98%，负氧离子含量是城区的20倍，景色优美。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567587725300.jpg\" title=\"1560567587725300.jpg\" alt=\"14.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">北欧风格的木质别墅，坐落在绿树成荫的竹林之中，让游客置身于大自然的怀抱，享受四星级的呵护，让您体验高质量的山间睡眠，回归大自然。这里是你向往的生活，那里没有雾霾，没有噪音，只有蓝天、白云、鸟语花香，享受着山间小屋的宁静，早晨打开门窗，看到花草的芬芳，闻到到处都是清香。</p><p><br/></p>',190,0,NULL),(36,1,'走进宝丰县王堂村，仿佛我又回到了童年的记忆，中午落座农家乐',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560567827','/uploads/20190615/f59a5dc2178d49cbba6d39fdea6b3b04.jpg','<p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: left;\">王堂村位于宝丰县城西7公里，这个村是一个只有560人、980亩土地的平原小村。近年来，在县里大力倡导乡村旅游的政策鼓励下，村里党员干部带头，以党建为引领，依据原始村貌，因地制宜，有效的把改善农村人居环境和农村传统民俗风情自然对接，保留住记载历史的老物件、老房子，充分利用农村传统文化，以村民持股方式搞起了民俗旅游。如今，村容村貌发生了较大变化，每逢周末，都会吸引着平顶山的市民到这里休闲游玩，村里的农家乐十分红火。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810339283.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810339283.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810320765.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810320765.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810829129.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810829129.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810484081.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810484081.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810888193.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810888193.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810885721.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810885721.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810160612.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810160612.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810376553.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810376553.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810446785.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810446785.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810148707.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810148707.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810477354.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810477354.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567810268053.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567810268053.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811337458.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811337458.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811339128.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811339128.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811444332.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811444332.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811532974.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811532974.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811482260.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811482260.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811344010.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811344010.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811107710.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811107710.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811965918.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811965918.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811974240.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811974240.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811868920.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811868920.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811853998.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811853998.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811183905.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811183905.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811366338.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811366338.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567811451324.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567811451324.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812312925.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812312925.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812900112.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812900112.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812598289.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812598289.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812995006.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812995006.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812146543.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812146543.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812575611.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812575611.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812251883.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812251883.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812738865.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812738865.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812854706.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812854706.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567812594778.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1560567812594778.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><br/></p>',131,0,NULL),(37,1,'荒坡变果园，叶县杨令庄村发展乡村旅游这么干……',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560567948','/uploads/20190615/e416985c76a11c1ea944451dc090717f.jpg','<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">3月27日，保安镇杨令庄村一处田埂旁，一台挖掘机正在挖沟铺设自来水管道。“村上要把种果树的田地全部通上自来水，便于灌溉。”该村村委会主任汪志平说。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567917153281.jpg\" title=\"1560567917153281.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">去年10月份，该村号召村民调整种植结构，大规模种植果树。截至目前，全村共发展梨树种植近千亩，加之以前发展的桃、杏、板栗等林果，共计1200亩。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">杨令庄村处于叶县南部，属浅山丘陵区，是一个移民村，耕地面积1600亩，林地面积4500亩，境内有黄花寺、椅子圈两座小型水库。2016年8月，该村被省政府移民办、省旅游局确定为省级乡村旅游试点村。河南大学旅游规划院为该村编制了旅游度假区总体规划和详细规划。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567927830003.jpg\" title=\"1560567927830003.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">新栽的梨树</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">依托优越的地理位置和丰富的自然资源，该村确定了林果种植、小杂粮种植、乡村旅游、风力发电四大支柱产业，实施乡村振兴。为发展林果种植，该村成立了杨令庄种植专业合作社，采取“合作社+农户”模式，统一种植、统一管理、统一销售；聘请保安镇官庄村黄金梨种植大户赵朝阳做技术指导，到村里为群众指导果树种植；组织党员、群众代表到官庄村以及方城、舞钢、鲁山等地参观考察。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567943943799.jpg\" title=\"1560567943943799.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">赵朝阳向村民传授梨树种植技术</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">“通过听课和实地考察，很多党员、群众的思想都被炒热了。”汪志平说，村干部带头发展，他自己就种了十几亩黄金梨。今年1月份，全村一次性种植梨树700余亩。为彻底解决果农的后顾之忧，村里承诺为所有果园铺设自来水管道，目前已投资5万余元，辐射果园200余亩。为支持该村发展林果业，县林业局还准备投资建设一座500吨的冷库。</p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560567939988396.jpg\" title=\"1560567939988396.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">通到田间的自来水</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">“我们村发展林果业的潜力尽管很大，但还有不少村民持观望态度。”汪志平说，他们正在商量，组织更多群众到安徽砀山参加那里一年一度的梨花节。“走出去，多见世面才能拓展发展思路。”</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">“种植果树既能让村民在土地上提质增效，也可以助推乡村旅游发展，几年后，我们村也能春赏花、秋收果了。”汪志平说。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">（赵贝贝）</p><p><br/></p>',143,0,NULL),(38,1,'叶县新地标50米高摩天轮正在吊装，游乐美食城即将闪亮登场！',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560568256','/uploads/20190615/6caf86bdcc00779f802b293d2b6a67c1.jpg','<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">叶县有哪些娱乐场地？</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">如果以前有人问你</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">你肯定会回答：公园和大广场</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">如果现在还有人问你</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">你一定会自豪的说</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">亿联游乐美食城和摩天轮</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568106649265.jpg\" title=\"1560568106649265.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">是的，现在全叶县</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">谁还不知道亿联建材五金城</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">谁还不知道亿联游乐美食城</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">谁还不知道鹰城之眼-摩天轮</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568117202814.jpg\" title=\"1560568117202814.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">五金建材城初见成效</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">游乐美食城拔地而起</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">地标摩天轮耀世瞩目</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">亿联控股扎根叶县</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">再添新城</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">携年度扛鼎力作</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">亿联游乐美食城</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">风范再临</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">为叶县城市建设发展增光添彩</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568124995139.jpg\" title=\"1560568124995139.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">亿联儿童游乐美食城，是2018年亿联控股集团扎根叶县又一力作。项目占地面积2万余平方米，建筑面积1万平方米，以儿童产业为主题，业态涵盖学前教育培训、儿童游乐、餐饮美食等三大业态为主，集“吃喝玩乐购教”儿童游乐亲子教育于一体，打造平顶山大型儿童主题乐园。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">户外游乐项目：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">摩天轮、狂呼、旋转木马、空中飞翔、音乐快车、旱冰场</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">室内儿童乐园：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">室内海洋球、VR互动体验、电玩、智力游戏、室内射击、网咖</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">亲子早教：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">传统手工艺、亲子早教、益智开发、亲子DIY、才艺培训、幼儿园</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">儿童产业：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">育婴馆、室内游泳馆、儿童摄影、儿童玩具、影楼</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">餐饮美食：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">时尚快餐、冷饮美食；特色小吃</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568135132945.jpg\" title=\"1560568135132945.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">儿童主题乐园，以儿童娱乐游玩为主题，集“吃喝玩乐购”儿童游玩亲子中心，50m高摩天轮、梦幻旋转木马、太空梭、旋转飞椅、极限碰碰车、疯狂海盗船... ... 让你不必远赴郑州、天津，在家门口就能体验到梦幻摩天轮的魅力，以及儿童乐园的欢乐和刺激！</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">小编，嫩跟俺们说说，这游乐城到底盖里咋样了？俺捉急呀，都想去玩里 …</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">小伙们莫着急，下面请看小编在施工现场发回的“施工进度”报道。</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568161711888.jpg\" title=\"1560568161711888.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">空前规划50m高摩天轮游乐设施，以设备稀缺性和极具昭示性，打造平顶山区域内地标性“鹰城之眼”！</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568171851147.jpg\" title=\"1560568171851147.jpg\" alt=\"6.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">工人师傅正在赶进度，涂装和装吊舱。</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568177312066.jpg\" title=\"1560568177312066.jpg\" alt=\"7.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">留心的小伙伴们都已经发现了，摩天轮已经初具成型，亭亭玉立的“鹰城之眼”已经映入眼帘啦！有木有很期待呀！</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568192569679.jpg\" title=\"1560568192569679.jpg\" alt=\"9.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">不过</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">小编偷偷告诉你，</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">到时这里建成的摩天轮将会是平顶山目前离地最高的，</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">超过50米（约20层楼高），</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">从最高处可以俯望到整个叶县！</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568207737078.jpg\" title=\"1560568207737078.jpg\" alt=\"10.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">“鹰城之眼”名不虚传</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568214357567.jpg\" title=\"1560568214357567.jpg\" alt=\"11.jpg\"/></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">因为小编就在这里最近的地方上班，能够第一时间，观察到施工进度。</p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">路过的小伙伴眼中是这样的！</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">远看近看都是那么好看</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>',189,0,NULL),(39,1,'春游走起！河南最美的十八个村庄全在这！咱平顶山就占2个！',NULL,'象眼旅游',50,1,'1560569667','/uploads/20190615/bc62a9819fe166a6b15dd3665fc85323.jpg','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">阳光灿烂的日子里</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">不出去浪</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">简直对不起这春光</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">随着温度的升高</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">小伙伴们可以计划一下<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">选一个好日子去春游了</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">这两年，乡村旅游火了起来<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">如果您不想在景区的拥挤中消耗体力</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">不妨到具有浓郁文化的古村落</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">寻找、探秘中原文明的印记</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;今天小编为大家精选<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">18个最美的乡村</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\">咱们一个个走起~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"outer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88655\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 2.5em; height: 2.5em; border-width: 2px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(206, 180, 141);\"></section><section style=\"margin: -2em 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: right; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、郑州<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">西泰山村</span></strong></section></section></section><p><br/></p></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568902237594.jpg\" title=\"1560568902237594.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em;\">在郑州有一座村庄叫西泰山村，村内有，千稼集、黄帝会盟祠、观音禅寺、日月潭、领军人物园、大汉地宫、美女岛、马武寨等景点星罗棋布。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568911584383.jpg\" title=\"1560568911584383.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 32px;\">每年五月，樱桃成熟，泰山村都会举行盛大的樱桃节，吃农家饭，住农家屋，其乐无穷。</span></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"outer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88655\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 2.5em; height: 2.5em; border-width: 2px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(206, 180, 141);\"></section><section style=\"margin: -2em 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: right; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、信阳<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">郝堂村</span></strong></section></section></section><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568920168670.jpg\" title=\"1560568920168670.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">在信阳市平桥区有一座村庄叫郝堂村，四面环山，空气清新，环境优美。狗头门楼、清水墙，用木头垛起的柴扉，彰显豫南山乡民居的风格。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568928163560.jpg\" title=\"1560568928163560.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px;\">依水的小桥，桥下流水潺潺;精心修葺的土坯房，翠竹掩映，溪水环绕，被外界称为“画家画出来的村庄”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568935335038.jpg\" title=\"1560568935335038.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"outer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" d