y: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560568948976483.jpg\" title=\"1560568948976483.jpg\" alt=\"7.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px;\">神秘的历史传说加上重渡沟的景区三绝。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560569856491729.jpg\" title=\"1560569856491729.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190615113723.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一绝是水</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px;\">，上百个泉眼数百股泉水汇成了兰溪清流。</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">二绝是竹</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px;\">，铺天盖地的万亩竹林形成一座天然画廊。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">三绝是农家宾馆</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 32px;\">，富有山情风味分布于竹海清流之中。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190615/1560569864188786.jpg\" title=\"1560569864188786.jpg\" alt=\"8.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"outer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88655\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !im